"""
    Convert a Graph to a GraphModel, setting graph_id and graph_version on all nodes.

    Args:
        creatable_graph (Graph): The creatable graph to convert.
        user_id (str): The ID of the user creating the graph.

    Returns:
        GraphModel: The converted Graph object.
    """
return GraphModel(**creatable_graph.model_dump(exclude={'nodes'}), user_id=
    user_id, nodes=[NodeModel(**creatable_node.model_dump(), graph_id=
    creatable_graph.id, graph_version=creatable_graph.version) for
    creatable_node in creatable_graph.nodes])
